eat in this Country. Nevertheless, I am still always relieved to find one.There does not appear to be a pool at the hotel (there is a great one on the top floor of Hotel Urban) and the gym is currently closed. You could take a run in the nearby Retiro Mediodia park if you feel the urge.Would I stay there again? Definitely. Would I take my family there next time? Definitely. RCL. 
